The 1st Annual Festival of Lights
A Miraculous Evening for the whole family to enjoy one candle at a time. 
Hosted and produced by Monogram Music Group international recording artist Liyah Bey. Liyah will welcome us into a star-studded evening with a variety of entertainment, comedy, and cooking all around a Jewish Holiday of spirituality founded on a true miracle. A musical night that will include songs by Eden Farber, and the Voice of Heart children’s choir,  as well as a special performance from Liyah,
She will introduce you to a wonderful group of celebrities including Sylvester Stallone, Jon Voight, Adam Sandler, and Rob Shnider all who will send you special wishes to make your Chanukah 8 nights to remember. 
The evening will be broadcast into 50  million homes by JLTV through their affiliates that include Dish Network, Spectrum, and digital apps like Apple TV and Roku.  will be you just need to believe.

The @WomenInMedia Holiday Toast has become synonymous with inspiration, community, and kicking off the festive season. This year, we were at the iconic Television City Studios in Hollywood.  We recognized truly legendary women who are making a mark in the entertainment industry, paving the way for greater female participation above and below the line.
